@@ -0,0 +1,148 @@
+/*
+ *  Gumstix SMC911x chip intialization driver
+ *
+ *  Author:     Craig Hughes
+ *  Created:    December 9, 2004
+ *  Copyright:  (C) 2004 Craig Hughes
+ *
